    "originContent": "**kirsch** /ˈkɪərʃ/ _n._",
    "translatedContent": "**kirsch** /ˈkɪərʃ/ _名詞_"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "6Y4lhC+A7l3KRG2Fls5ju9BL98HzvUrKbiMxTb+GCow=",
    "originContent": "1. _(German)_ cherry.",
    "translatedContent": "1. _(ドイツ語)_ サクランボ。"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "P3izapO3lqAo+wUfe/kPpHLMp/0YwDKE7qbmRREH+Jw=",
    "originContent": "1. _(Russell A. Kirsch, 1929 - 2020)_ American engineer recognized as the",
    "translatedContent": "1. _(ラッセル・A・カース、1929 - 2020)_ 初のデジタル画像スキャナの開発者であり、ピクセルの発明者として知られるアメリカの技術者。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "jGuinQSptE9x7FzrM2y5Eoyw+VwUQr3kCwep9vMO5Ws=",
    "originContent": "   developer of the first digital image scanner and the inventor of the pixel.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "1. 6x16のバウンディングボックス（平均幅5px、ベースラインからの下がり4px、上昇12px、x-ハイト5px、キャップハイト9px）を持つ等幅ビットマップフォント。様々な書体やモチーフから引き出し、小さなサイズで独特のヒューマニスト感を作り出しています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "IncGzAokxEnXu3JFIV9J+vD+e26Kf0oHhcJ+brSadhE=",
    "originContent": "1. A monospace bitmap font with a 6x16 bounding box (5px avg width, 4px descent,",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "gxKx0QkE2/pqd2mn9l8vx5LgKe01oU3CBAhNDJbr5z0=",
    "originContent": "   12px ascent, 5px x-height, 9px cap height). It draws from a variety of",
    "translatedContent": "   一部のグリフは[Cozette](https://github.com/slavfox/Cozette)由来で、kirschのデザインに合わせてしばしば修正されています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "Dr8K9qHEbwfV2OG4lmqxAACZrOmGLh2Ce59H3nSfDj4=",
    "originContent": "   letterforms and motifs to create a distinct humanist feel at a compact size.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "9SWxlS9i/EGOmsiff3g3RT0vNm1Bx/fmojqDMRrUgzI=",
    "originContent": "   Some glyphs come from [Cozette](https://github.com/slavfox/Cozette), often",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "TyJXaZBA6nGVSctZoQD2trGZy6Pj1UAN6WRi3oPoyTo=",
