  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "EKRy54WN/ciI+IacIbbgeR3KP0Kh9IXX1GpYSplvd8g=",
    "originContent": "## Installation/Usage",
    "translatedContent": "## インストール／使用方法"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "cSsPFK0VMwG3PDyEOuERVSzqnY6xlysd9PKvSHS8yYY=",
    "originContent": "Download from [Releases](https://github.com/molarmanful/kirsch/releases).",
    "translatedContent": "[Releases](https://github.com/molarmanful/kirsch/releases) からダウンロードしてください。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "RRfY8AfRcCzPiIPmvARHlJGNcXXasGNhg/Vwljwrxho=",
    "originContent": "Included are bitmap formats - OTB, BDF, PCF, DFONT (for Mac users) - as well as",
    "translatedContent": "含まれているのはビットマップ形式のOTB、BDF、PCF、DFONT（Macユーザー向け）と  "
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "3fUqBjxB/bnOAutUnZXv2RrnmV6aGzdN6ZMD8SMNkpk=",
    "originContent": "TTF. 2x versions are available for HiDPI screens. Note that PCF doesn't contain",
    "translatedContent": "TTFです。HiDPI画面用に2倍サイズのバージョンもあります。PCFはU+FFFF以降の  "
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "TtzhK+rJQ7UETumcsfSTF8U8ah6amJn7Pm/HSPZtA84=",
    "originContent": "glyphs past U+FFFF.",
    "translatedContent": "グリフを含まないことに注意してください。"
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "BKUCXJBFxYhwGMjN+yqatMqWs4WIkN4qnP4WQbzIkkg=",
    "originContent": "For the crispiest viewing experience, try to use the bitmap formats when",
    "translatedContent": "最も鮮明な表示を得るには、可能な限りビットマップ形式を使用してください。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "JpRR6BaM+j9atlRRLCA1sD/toGtR+9n+OsUDNVIVlnU=",
    "originContent": "possible. If bitmap fonts are not supported on your platform (e.g. Windows,",
    "translatedContent": "プラットフォームでビットマップフォントがサポートされていない場合（例：Windows、VSCode）  "
  },
  {
    "row": 79,
    "rowsha": "nwTVuYFc0B6394hsjYVZ04LRbbziXY/ahJB9/HxfVTE=",
    "originContent": "VSCode), then use the TTF at font sizes that are multiples of 16px.",
    "translatedContent": "は、16pxの倍数のフォントサイズでTTFを使用してください。"
  },
  {
    "row": 80,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 81,
    "rowsha": "MMUlW+UIuv8EJ+CWFdds9MRASFdh7lKWBYOVgxwXgqM=",
    "originContent": "> [!TIP]",
    "translatedContent": "> [!TIP]"
  },
  {
    "row": 82,
    "rowsha": "Lxb2XjWnGcpePKRKFObhlY5bXh8v0YK8orV9swM8IXE=",
    "originContent": "> If you need font size in pt, use the following conversion:",
    "translatedContent": "> フォントサイズをptで指定する必要がある場合は、以下の変換式を使用してください："
  },
  {
    "row": 83,
    "rowsha": "YrZ+H2hbf+9RECAF3d0nd0vj/uOMQpZcU6qwNdC2siE=",
    "originContent": ">",
    "translatedContent": ">"
  },
  {
    "row": 84,
    "rowsha": "7anUr4CpoGqVo1zN3TGMiEIeOc8ypv1R6wdU/TSvjKI=",
    "originContent": "> `pt = px * 72 / dpi`",
    "translatedContent": "> `pt = px * 72 / dpi`"
  },
  {
    "row": 85,
    "rowsha": "YrZ+H2hbf+9RECAF3d0nd0vj/uOMQpZcU6qwNdC2siE=",
    "originContent": ">",
    "translatedContent": ">"
  },
  {
    "row": 86,
    "rowsha": "FjgbBZUousj4aH+Stn00KZkDlNTpcxLe2SkrrRxX3nM=",
    "originContent": "> e.g. 16px on a 96dpi screen is `16px * 72 / 96dpi = 12pt`.",
    "translatedContent": "> 例：96dpiの画面で16pxは `16px * 72 / 96dpi = 12pt` となります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 87,
