    "originContent": "### Nerd Fonts",
    "translatedContent": "### Nerd Fonts"
  },
  {
    "row": 89,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 90,
    "rowsha": "uJBJusYwPANmMUn2iDKvFhB3wGXjympeP3eMlBHkAKA=",
    "originContent": "kirsch comes with custom Nerd Fonts glyphs. Support is still WIP. For the sake",
    "translatedContent": "kirschにはカスタムNerd Fontsのグリフが含まれています。サポートはまだ作業中です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 91,
    "rowsha": "mnGYq4eW5577PCLz3lnqPDvkAEXGVfCoSRbd01hJwPc=",
    "originContent": "of visual clarity, kirsch's Nerd Fonts glyphs tend to bleed heavily beyond their",
    "translatedContent": "視覚的な明瞭さのために、kirschのNerd Fontsグリフは幅を大きく超えてはみ出す傾向があります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 92,
    "rowsha": "AnvNIt2M3V2gldJW1HUmPvRK9cq5iPnNL1sCGTvbAmk=",
    "originContent": "widths. I've drawn these glyphs with the expectation that they will look best",
    "translatedContent": "これらのグリフは、前後にスペースを1つずつ入れてパディングすると最も見栄えが良くなるように設計されています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 93,
    "rowsha": "BDkcTo/hb5W11OUwygfF4A2UmBTu7K+d3GLxAicCqAM=",
    "originContent": "when padded before and after with a single space.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 94,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "Nerd Fontsの残りをカバーするパッチ済みNerd Fontsも利用可能です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "Z4BMEJoRl9qo0Z0PjQgbTmgu4WA9z+6/b4SQ/4K985M=",
    "originContent": "Patched Nerd Fonts that cover the rest of the Nerd Fonts are available. The",
    "translatedContent": "\"Mono\"バリアントはより小さなグリフ（幅がダブルではなくシングル）を使用し、"
  },
  {
    "row": 96,
    "rowsha": "4vwx1wAaA8m8ByvR4Am5P4wF2UmfpoTzx7t83qWgw8I=",
    "originContent": "\"Mono\" variant uses smaller glyphs (single- instead of double-width) and works",
    "translatedContent": "幅が混在できない端末でも動作します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "86kGlSQmdJ8PEEraIjFLGxCpPD8JBkwdfAsmLQU0bwY=",
    "originContent": "for terminals that can't mix widths.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### Propo"
