  {
    "row": 114,
    "rowsha": "q6wuWvW7Ze0hl/RCQyyhBnuPhx04puR1hMw9O/JqDWo=",
    "originContent": "`default`) is the base package, while `kirsch-nerd` includes Nerd Fonts patches.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 115,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### Web"
  },
  {
    "row": 116,
    "rowsha": "Kpl17XpHCn0xpBlB+Ldte8K91xwlKtplgoaVl3hfDLI=",
    "originContent": "### Web",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 117,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "ビットマップ対応がないため、一般的にはWebでのkirschの使用は推奨しません。"
  },
  {
    "row": 118,
    "rowsha": "jg6/Sv1WFtMPfBinOvrzmXNmznhH7hLQ6yC5hIHjEmo=",
    "originContent": "I would generally discourage usage of kirsch on the web due to lack of bitmap",
    "translatedContent": "しかし、頑固で勇敢な方のためにWOFF2が利用可能です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 119,
    "rowsha": "QTR/y9VuS4pZTAjdnyaAOMdEST8/yNi6/Cu4q1e9x+M=",
    "originContent": "support. But for the stubborn and the brave, WOFF2 is available. There is also a",
    "translatedContent": "また、[CDNホストのスタイルシート](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/kirsch@latest/kirsch.css)もあります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 120,
    "rowsha": "ejyuKgUo16SumTW8sin5hf+JOFadOdGUt5K/ZFph9so=",
    "originContent": "[CDN-hosted stylesheet](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/kirsch@latest/kirsch.css)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 121,
    "rowsha": "mCThJvcJNN01LIadxlzxo1bLIJAy5izaKeIaUd6kutQ=",
    "originContent": "for convenience.",
    "translatedContent": "便宜のため。"
  },
  {
    "row": 122,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 123,
    "rowsha": "Uc5+AjuMoqnnDSvMf+9u+CTVledsHCbqDg0MxKvxsYw=",
    "originContent": "```html",
    "translatedContent": "```html"
  },
  {
    "row": 124,
    "rowsha": "TosDlmsxDcNG8Ly2PNaJ2Y3ItvFn5WzA1coZ45Kli/4=",
    "originContent": "<link",
    "translatedContent": "<link"
  },
  {
    "row": 125,
    "rowsha": "8bxKwVcdXOHE7/aZHOcfKs+HZ8q+9430mA/aE3CZTXc=",
    "originContent": "  rel=\"stylesheet\"",
    "translatedContent": "  rel=\"stylesheet\""
  },
  {
