    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## デザインノート"
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "zxPDZVvxF7NbnUvikvApd6uE47lalJ7Qx/+8iGtBz4U=",
    "originContent": "## Design Notes",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "前作のフォント [eldur](https://github.com/molarmanful/eldur) は平均文字幅がわずか4pxだったのに対し、kirsch は平均文字幅が5pxです。その1pxの余裕がデザインに驚くほどの柔軟性をもたらします。5px幅に快適に収まるグリフがはるかに多く、例えば「m」や「w」などはカーニングを壊すことなく隣接グリフのスペースに侵入しません。5px幅に収まらないグリフは7px幅で扱うことができ、バランスと判読性を維持しつつカーニングに悪影響を及ぼしません。"
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "Mf3ezTi+Lfv9XdblyIQAiXhISBs/Js26pes/OhdZpIk=",
    "originContent": "Unlike my previous font [eldur](https://github.com/molarmanful/eldur), which had",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "R8gALuqwPO313CMg7xNyh8VFyBrFlFq2sMmEqi6kmAQ=",
    "originContent": "a mere 4px avg. char width to work with, kirsch has a 5px avg. char width. That",
    "translatedContent": "### フローリッシュ"
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "85/CmRZSW8+32ui3v4HKMW+A+iDUmBUCPJsTHEX/63w=",
    "originContent": "1px of extra width affords a surprising amount of leeway for the design. Far",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "rK0s4Q/fhrraSvYkWSlq4AKb6qx1rvLzJEnxHSIwd9w=",
    "originContent": "more glyphs fit comfortably into 5px width - e.g. \"m\" and \"w\" - meaning that",
    "translatedContent": "![rogue fijian xylophone](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/molarmanful/kirsch/main/./img/design-flourishes.png)"
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "lNP7/RTezTbOh5+i51kPVLa59m+K0kmrgOpVXMV1n0A=",
    "originContent": "those glyphs won't break kerning and intrude on the spaces of neighboring",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "Nsqn44N+b/qTxIvR7q591Kdt9WbABvC481j2gjsD5nY=",
    "originContent": "glyphs. Glyphs that don't fit into 5px width can now work with 7px width, which",
    "translatedContent": "フローリッシュ（例えば「i」や「f」の飾り）はスタイリスティックな選択ですが、機能的な役割も果たします。フローリッシュがなければ「i」は1px幅しか使わず、4pxの中途半端な空白が残ります。「i」の両側に2pxずつのフローリッシュを付けることで5px幅となり、スタイリッシュにカーニング問題を解決します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "dQN0ce/QLnweUCW9z64o2ignuXrIMmMkt3u9gQT1KlQ=",
    "originContent": "maintains balance and legibility without affecting kerning too negatively.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "「l」の場合は、スクリプトスタイルのフローリッシュが他の縦長文字（`1I|`など）との差別化をさらに強化します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "b3jliIH3+E7k3iZ/1a/A4kqibY0bGCK71bvwqt44CdA=",
    "originContent": "### Flourishes",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### ギャップ"
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "8PYN67dJT/H00SI4lfS6KljiadmSWSnLH1L8xEzpNJY=",
    "originContent": "![rogue fijian xylophone](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/molarmanful/kirsch/main/./img/design-flourishes.png)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 143,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "![bad queen peg 69](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/molarmanful/kirsch/main/./img/design-gaps.png)"
  },
  {
    "row": 144,
    "rowsha": "vP8sH24QoBSU0jB1YBXjT89oqE7yUQDKXnPHQ5Ql7SE=",
    "originContent": "The flourishes - e.g. in \"i\" or \"f\" - are a stylistic choice, but they also",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 145,
    "rowsha": "EQLBbhWsnB7fu1L5F6mn3K2O9VqCyinGF/aPznjLsLo=",
    "originContent": "serve a functional purpose. Without the flourishes, \"i\" would take up 1px of",
    "translatedContent": "kirsch の特徴的な要素の一つは文字のボウル部分にギャップがあることです。ギャップを埋めると文字が四角くなりすぎたり詰まりすぎたりしますが、ギャップを開けておくことで文字の形状がすっきりします。このギャップはスクリプトスタイルのストロークの終端も想起させます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 146,
    "rowsha": "Y0UdEQ8ZbtsQLURubpBbHcPrsG5tEGoBNTSbbAFNwZM=",
    "originContent": "width, leaving 4px of awkward space. 2px flourishes on each side of the \"i\" give",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
    "rowsha": "kPFA5L2EgGyAjYYB9L1NBm1dG+dwmUGj7A/Qsw/69/M=",
    "originContent": "it a 5px width, thereby addressing the kerning issue in a stylish way.",
    "translatedContent": "## 貢献"
  },
  {
    "row": 148,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 149,
    "rowsha": "cGET9TYoRNhIFvrvFAAGo1NWA3CvMBVg1X0iiwL5bjc=",
    "originContent": "In \"l\"'s case, the script-style flourishes further distinguish it from other",
    "translatedContent": "イシュー、機能やグリフのリクエスト、プルリクエストは大歓迎です！フォントファイルは [bited](https://github.com/molarmanful/bited) を使って編集しています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 150,
    "rowsha": "QK7LwujwdHNiJoHvQVhSsvZSiLjO+nBsVyaaugo/zXQ=",
    "originContent": "vertical characters like `1I|`.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 151,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## クレジット"
  },
  {
    "row": 152,
    "rowsha": "XYX1EsNnuubAHE4azCpMOBbpOBk+ZPhpLlOML70VHRE=",
    "originContent": "### Gaps",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 153,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "これらのプロジェクトはkirschの作成にインスピレーションや助けを与えてくれたものであり、完全に価値があります"
  },
  {
    "row": 154,
    "rowsha": "2h97dSmxwd2gD66rqDqvZFVBw98Oh0+GFn+qXUpddRU=",
    "originContent": "![bad queen peg 69](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/molarmanful/kirsch/main/./img/design-gaps.png)",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 155,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 156,
    "rowsha": "GLvwnfLpF75J8NucQRIY98Q+3nbFp9dEbdYZjoNOAyY=",
    "originContent": "One of kirsch's distinctive features is the presence of a gap at the bowls of",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 157,
    "rowsha": "0wyaEB/fDcYvLo43T/OclNyFdKq8st0BTytZgmqx4s0=",
    "originContent": "the letters. Filling in the gap would make the letters either too square or too",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 158,
    "rowsha": "Tx7op5OR6XnOTNYn/1dUqbaeWRkXSrgAke7jt4sWlfc=",
    "originContent": "bunched-up, while leaving the gap open declutters the letterforms. The gaps also",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 159,
    "rowsha": "sJmwmbKrT0gpqAGo7kaBhTCX8oM7/l1PN+m1stau2TY=",
    "originContent": "evoke script-style stroke endings.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 160,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 161,
    "rowsha": "R5ZPLZ4vkE9tjX5qe8QB7AkTfWZsuNTGFLFKMp2KUzM=",
    "originContent": "## Contributing",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 162,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 163,
    "rowsha": "LnGzk0p1UFdzDydq/31ADkoQYC2QXxwNOaap8rw64CI=",
    "originContent": "Issues, feature/glyph requests, and pull requests are all welcome! Font files",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 164,
    "rowsha": "b76l4fZTl5GtAiqTE7RMBs9yHjiTK6yzvSFkdbhDpSQ=",
    "originContent": "are edited via [bited](https://github.com/molarmanful/bited).",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 165,
